    • inclusionPredicate

      public static Predicate<org.springframework.boot.actuate.audit.AuditEvent> inclusionPredicate(List<String> types)
      Returns an audit event filter that accepts a list of event types that are accepted.

      If the types parameter is null or an empty list, all events are accepted.

      Parameters:
      types - the types that are accepted
      Returns:
      a Predicate that returns true if an event should be audited

    • exclusionPredicate

      public static Predicate<org.springframework.boot.actuate.audit.AuditEvent> exclusionPredicate(List<String> types)
      Returns an audit event filter that excludes the given event types from being audited.

      If the types parameter is null or an empty list, no events are excluded.

      Parameters:
      types - the types to exclude
      Returns:
      a Predicate that returns true if an event should be audited

    • inclusionExclusionPredicate

      public static Predicate<org.springframework.boot.actuate.audit.AuditEvent> inclusionExclusionPredicate(List<String> includeTypes, List<String> dontIncludeTypes)
      Returns an audit event filter that combines inclusionExclusionPredicate(List, List) and exclusionPredicate(List).
      Parameters:
      includeTypes - the types to include (if null or empty, all events are accepted)
      dontIncludeTypes - the types to exclude (if null or empty, no events are excluded)
      Returns:
      a Predicate that returns true if an event should be audited
